body:
H Grup IT Expert is looking for candidates for our new opening as a Project Manager on a Cobol application! 

Requirements: 
- Fluent in English;
- Leadership;
- Ability to delegate;
- Capacity of decision and responsibility;
- Ability to mobilize and to develop the team;
- Client and results orientation (professional goals in total); 
- Initiative;
- Team spirit;
-  Analytical thinking;
- Organizational and communication skills;
- ITIL basics are a plus;
- Mainframe and Cobol Knowledge with banking application in Cobol is a must;
- Bank and Consumer finance Knowledge;

Responsibilities: 
- Project Portfolio Management and application run activities
          -> Change management: Projects & Evolutions;
          -> Budget, Schedule, Quality, Risks;
- Incident & PB
          -> Report the incidents;
          -> Log incidents & problems;
          -> Follow the incidents opened and solve it according to the SLA;
- Production Monitoring
          -> Daily production check;
          -> Night duty plan and escalation;
- Service Request
          -> Ticket monitoring, classification, resolution time;
- Resources Management
          -> Ensure the full allocation of team members;
          -> Ensure the cohesion between team members;
          -> Ensure the knowledge increase of team members;
          -> Ensure the usage of internal process and procedures;
- Reporting
          -> Regular Activities reporting to its management and customers;

Our offer:
- Attractive and competitive salary package;
- Private healthcare package;
- Great work environment.

We are looking forward to have you in our team!
